{"tid":1761396,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"喜訊, 港航拖糧, 彩福減人工","createTime":"2019-11-29T01:42:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T03:35:26.000Z","uid":155883,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7f5577aabe3d78a52f0302ecdace6f6b301876a5","tid":1761396,"uid":155883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T01:42:17.000Z","msg":"明年加薪或僅2.7%<br />\n<br />\n報告指，2020年打工仔平均加薪幅度預計僅得2.7%，而加薪幅度最高的行業為電訊（5%）、電子商務（4.8%）及醫療/製藥（4.1%）。減薪個案方面，彩福婚宴集團昨日向員工發聲明指，11月及12月份全體員工薪酬下調5%，但未披露明年的薪酬安排。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20191129/I6BB7J67WICZ6ANRSSV5YZBEKU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20191129%2FI6BB7J67WICZ6ANRSSV5YZBEKU%2F&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLaha%2BoeUeRXR1jLQ0PybHu0%3D&h=6b727641\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20191129%2FI6BB7J67WICZ6ANRSSV5YZBEKU%2F&h=7392010d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20191129/I6BB7J67WICZ6ANRSSV5YZBEKU/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20191129/EE3LEUJDIPUDBIT5YEXNCRGF2E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20191129%2FEE3LEUJDIPUDBIT5YEXNCRGF2E%2F&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLaha%2BoeUeRXR1jLQ0PybHu0%3D&h=4ebd5d47\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20191129%2FEE3LEUJDIPUDBIT5YEXNCRGF2E%2F&h=f7d056cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/20191129/EE3LEUJDIPUDBIT5YEXNCRGF2E/</a><br />\n電郵中指，除機艙服務員及駐海外的員工，在港的所有員工本月薪金，將由原定於本月最後一天出糧，延遲至下月6日才發放。公司對此深表歉意，並希望員工繼續支持公司渡過考驗及難關。<br />\n<br />\n香港航空本月支薪日期需再延遲至下月6日。資料圖片<br />\n強調屬一次性安排<br />\n<br />\n港航回覆本報查詢時承認事件，惟強調安排屬一次性，並不會影響公司的日常運作，又指員工仍然會以專業的態度，為顧客提供安全及暢順的服務。港航亦再次把業績下滑歸咎於近月本港社會運動及旅遊需求疲弱。事實上，港航資金鏈出現問題早於去年8月起由股東之間爭拗中見端倪，加上屢被商業夥伴「追債」，財困問題絕非近月才出現。<br />\n<br />\n此外，港航已並非首次「拖糧」。公司今年8月已發出通知，指9月起每月的支薪日將延遲至每月的最後一天；今年9月，港航再度表示，由於近期香港發生的事件導致旅遊需求下降，為進一步減省公司營運開支，管理層團隊由2019年9月至12月，將連續四個月減薪20%，並呼籲員工放無薪假。"},{"pid":"61ac4723d9c04692d2a1f511f2b717cda8876f61","tid":1761396,"uid":49643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T01:51:20.000Z","msg":"港航好似本來都唔係好掂，係咪借d易呀"},{"pid":"9e7803264d4598441f4a9f8788f1a35a258da674","tid":1761396,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T01:53:13.000Z","msg":"彩福婚宴集團<br />\n做結婚扮咩呀"},{"pid":"d0f067e0d8657ab7d791063ec25b61e1a8d0e8d3","tid":1761396,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T01:57:00.000Z","msg":"此外，港航已並非首次「拖糧」。公司今年8月已發出通知，指9月起每月的支薪日將延遲至每月的最後一天<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似係之前早出啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16393d28406e6093c7104604434c41271c03cfb0","tid":1761396,"uid":759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T01:57:54.000Z","msg":"可以減人工既咩"},{"pid":"d75c77750747c39a3d383928eebebd320b48ad28","tid":1761396,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T03:35:26.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}